# RapidAPI key for SkiAPI (ski-api.p.rapidapi.com). Free tier: ~500 requests/month.
# 1. Create a free account at https://rapidapi.com
# 2. Subscribe to the SkiAPI free tier
# 3. Copy your key below, then copy this file to `.env` (which is gitignored)
#
# Enables the direct "Resort Report" (lift/trail status) for SkiAPI-backed
# resorts: Heavenly, Kirkwood, Boreal, and Diamond Peak. Leave it blank to skip
# those calls — weather data and free sources (Palisades, Northstar, Sugar Bowl)
# keep working without a key.
#
# SECURITY NOTE: TahoeSno is a static client app, so any value here is bundled
# into the public client JavaScript and is visible to end users. Only use a
# free-tier, low-risk key here. For a secret key, proxy SkiAPI through a backend.
VITE_RAPIDAPI_KEY=
